fuzzySymbols

Class FuzzySymbolicVariableConstraintSolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • framework.ConstraintSolver
      • fuzzySymbols.FuzzySymbolicVariableConstraintSolver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class FuzzySymbolicVariableConstraintSolver
extends ConstraintSolver
    This ConstraintSolver solves CSPs where variables are fuzzy sets (see FuzzySymbolicVariable) and constraints are equality or inequalities among fuzzy sets. Constraints are crisp, and represented by SymbolicValueConstraints.
    Author:
    Masoumeh Mansouri
    See Also:
